<item>
            <title>[SOLR-3877] backup and snapshooter scripts do not work.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3877</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When trying to run the ./backup and ./snapshooter scripts, they do not work. It seems like they are looking for differently named files.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Are these deprecated or unsupported?&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
